    To prove the stability results for the Gaussian fermion problems, we utilize the fact that both equilibrium and dynamical properties of Gaussian fermion models can be captured by just the covariance matrix of the state at hand—more specifically, for a time-dependent Gaussian state

     ρ

    (

     t

    ), the corresponding covariance matrix is given by







