    and its dynamics, for the quantum simulator model with gaussian errors and noise sources described in results section, is derived in lemma 3 in supplemental note

     II

    . The stability result for dynamics (proposition 1) is obtained from an application of rigorous time-dependent perturbation theory on the effective equations of motion for the covariance matrix.

